# Training Animal Lore by Jaseowns
# UO Outlands
# Requirements:  
#   Run script and select an
#   animal target
#
# Additional Info: 
#   You will passively gain this skill taming
#   but if you wanted to speed it up use the following
#   script
setvar "my_training_target"
while skill "animallore" < 100
    useskill "animallore"
    wft 500
    target "my_training_target"
    wait 2000
endwhile